<section class="section">
    <div class="catalogo__container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h2 class="hero__title">{{usser}}
                üçî, Wellcome! Products Template page</h2>
            <p class="">
                In this section is shown a small demo collection, the purpuses
                is to show how pagination, limit and querys works, besides there
                is a small demo of add or remove products to the current user's
                shopping cart.
            </p>
            <h3 class="hero__lead">Ussage</h3>
            <p>
                With the products main endpoint you can mannage the data through
                the following querrys (remember use "/?").
            </p>
            <br />
            <ul class="info__list">
                <li>
                    <strong class="info__title">Limit and Page:</strong>
                    by default limit=10, page=1, this template uses it so you
                    can see how it works, this values define number of pages
                    avalible
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong class="info__title">Category:</strong>
                    Filters products by category, an example is
                    category=tortillas
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong class="info__title">Order:</strong>
                    Order the products by default in an ascend order, the
                    reference by default is price, example: order=1 (asc order),
                    order=-1 (desc order)
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong class="info__title">To:</strong>
                    Uses for refer another property diferent than price to order by in your querry, an example is order by title (to=title)
                </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>
                More information about the payload is detailed in
                <a
                    class="link link--branded"
                    href="https://github.com/AlexisPerdomoD/e-free"
                >E-free github Repository.</a>
            </p>

        </div>
        <div class="catalogo container">
            <div class="hero__content">
                <h4 class="hero__lead">Catalogo section</h4>
            </div>
            <ul class="catalogo__list">
                {{#checkList products}}
                    {{printProduct this}}
                {{/checkList}}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
